        public SyslogEventCollector withExpectation​(Predicate<Map<String,​Object>> predicate,
                                            int expectedElements)
        Wrap collector so that only dedicated syslog events are recorded and a number of expected elements can be defined. await(long, TimeUnit) will return true if the expected number of elements have been recorded.
        Parameters:
        predicate - Predicate returning true if the syslog event shall be recorded
        expectedElements - number of expected syslog records
        Returns:
        wrapped collector
